# Markdown files can contain lines that end in spaces.
#
# Two trailing spaces mean to insert a carriage return.
#
# Would be nice if we could do better and only allow two spaces, and not one,
# or three or more, but that's probably asking too much for git.
*.md        whitespace=-blank-at-eol
*.mdwn      whitespace=-blank-at-eol
*.markdown  whitespace=-blank-at-eol
